). The user also agrees to make sure all of its users agree to this policy as well as to all terms of this agreement before they use the service.
12.5.
If a user does not agree, Scanbooster is not required to offer any kind of compensation.
12.6.
The user also acknowledges that each user is required to accept all terms of this agreement as well as of the privacy policy on our website before being able to use the service or any of our offered apps.
12.7.
The Scanbooster account creation and use of the service shall be available only to users owning an email-address ending with the email address fixed beforehand.
12.8.
The creation of the user accounts described above as well as the hosting of the user accounts shall be included in the aforementioned license fee, paid by the user.
12.9.
It is strictly forbidden to use single user in-app subscriptions or purchases for instutional and or teaching purposes.
13.
Warranty and Refunds
13.1.
Scanbooster ultrasound sim is an app for medical professionals such as doctors, sonographers as well as medical students and other students. Its goal is to teach the art of performing sonography. To do this, Scanbooster uses real images for maximum realism and live-labeling to show what structures are currently displayed. It is NOT able to actually perform a real ultrasound examination on a real patient and it is neither able to transform your device into a real ultrasound machine. Neither is any other of our apps offered. All information contained within Scanbooster and any other app offered by us has been researched to the best of our knowledge and belief. It has been reviewed and tested extensively by leading German medical experts in their field to their full content. However, we cannot, and we do NOT assume liability of any kind for anything contained within the service and neither for any liabilities or harms that might result from using the service.
13.2.
The service is provided additionally under the terms of Apple’s end user license agreement for app downloads.
13.3 The service and all apps are offered solely on an "AS-IS" basis.
13.4 Since this is a service (
software as a service,
"SAAS"), no refunds will be offered.
14.
Final provisions
14.1.
If a provision of this Agreement is or becomes illegal, invalid or unenforceable in any jurisdiction, that shall not affect:
14.1.1.
the validity or enforceability in that jurisdiction of any other provision of this Agreement; or
14.1.2.
the validity or enforceability in other jurisdictions of that or any other provision of this Agreement.
14.2.
If applicable and if Scanbooster fails to provide the aforementioned service during the licensing period, the user shall be given no compensation of any kind. Furthermore, Scanbooster possesses the right to change, delete or add any content to this agreement without prior consent. Furthermore, the service may end at any time without prior notice and without any compensation. Additionally, Scanbooster is not required to provide support and or help, updates, fixes for the apps of any kind. Scanbooster also has the right to take down any of its apps at any time without compensation of any kind and without prior notice of any kind.
14.3.
Scanbooster and user agree to all of the above and confirm that they have understood the customer agreement completely. This agreement shall be concluded for the same, aforementioned period of time, for which the user possesses access to the service. The user automatically agrees to the complete content of this agreement as well as our privacy policy, accessible on our website and all of their points by using, accessing any apps offered by Scanbooster, any service offered by Scanbooster and or any content offered by Scanbooster.
